      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "@YannC&#233;bron same here, with gradle. The file gets created in ./build/classes/java/main/META-INF/spring-configuration-meta&zwnj;&#8203;data.json, but IntelliJ doesn&#39;t take it into account. If I manually move the json file to src/main/resources/META-INF it works (the configs are no longer yellowed)"
