    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>For me, other answers didn't work. I had to go to open <code>Files</code> and do <code>Invalidate caches and restart</code> on Intellij. After that, everything worked fine again.</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 1463205,
      "reputation" : 517,
      "user_id" : 1376906,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 71,
      "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/vkROJ.png?s=256",
