    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>I just needed</p>\n<pre><code>@EnableConfigurationProperties({MY_PROPS_CLASS.class})\n</code></pre>\n<p>in Main Application class and it helped me to resolve this issue</p>\n"
